code: void assertCalled(List<Node> nodes) {     HttpHost[] hosts = new HttpHost[nodes.size()].     for (int i = 0. i < nodes.size(). i++) {         hosts[i] = nodes.get(i).getHost().     }     assertCalled(hosts). }
